text: Komsomolsky () is a rural locality (a selo) in Rassvetovsky Selsoviet, Davlekanovsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 259 as of 2010. There are 5 streets. == Geography == It is located 7 km from Davlekanovo, 7 km from Rassvet. == References == Category:Rural localities in Davlekanovsky District
title: Komsomolsky, Davlekanovsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
